channel.desc: The Beavers turn the page as they host the Leopards. Oregon State dismissed head coach Trent Bray on Oct. 12 after falling to 0-7 with a 39-14 loss to Wake Forest for its worst start since 1991. Lafayette's Kente Edwards has 10 rushing TDs this year.
